survey.music_making: Classically trained pianist playing from age 4-13, violinist from age 9-21, Conservatory trained (keyboard studies, music theory, ear training, etc.) from age 17-21
survey.activities: Administrative tasks, driving, cleaning dishes, completing chores
survey.habit_change: My musical tastes have evolved as I've gotten older and have been exposed to different things in life. For example, when I realized I was queer, I began really connecting more with LGBTQ+ artists and representation in music.
survey.habits: My spouse and I create a new Pandora station for ourselves each year. We start by populating it with our newest and latest favorite songs and/or artists, let the station get to know our tastes, and then use it to introduce new music to ourselves.
